item.title: Need help with something easy (not for me though)
item.dc:creator: @p_e_e_p_z_i p e e p z i
item.description:
@p_e_e_p_z_i wrote:

[quote=“WRX`, post:3, topic:227199”][quote author=p e e p z i link=topic=298551.msg2398024#msg2398024 date=1219270004]
Search one emote in the client.java and try to find it.
[/quote]

Wrong. hes asking how to sendquest, basically he needs the ID of them.

Get the ID’s of the button, for where the text should be sent, and it will be

sendQuest("text to go on button", ID);

Note: The ID to send text ISN’T the same as the button clicking ID.[/quote]

Thanks for correcting me.
